reviewText: Not as kid friendly as I would have liked

My daughter enjoyed the DVD but i was dissapointed to find a spelling mistake on what is a childs educational video.
On the menu with the names of the clips, they have spelt balloons as ballons. A rediculous mistake that shouldn't happen.
My son LOVED the video on youtube, and I followed the link and purchased the video for his birthday. It is NOT the same video!

I purchased this for my two year old granddaughter after seeing her reaction to some of the music on Utube. She loves all of the music and she sings along as the video plays. It is a great purchase for any toddler or preschooler.
